System:

    melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms

Usage:

To run and restart with script:

    ./run

    Output from original in n/out/ and from restart in n/rst/

To run independent MC simulations on 3 processors:

    mpirun -np 3 mcSim_m -e -p param -c commands

    (See files n/log, n=0,1, 2 for log output)

Restarting above:

    mpirun -np 3 mcSim_m -e -p param -c commands


